      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "text": "FUNCTIONAL\nREQUIREMENTS: 1Min\n\nIn-SCOPE: \n1. saving customer payment\ndetails\n 2.  Making payment (in-\nflow)\n3. Payment outflow to\nsponsored partners\n4. Option to reuse / add\n5. Analytics dashboard\nLeast, most, how many\ntimes\n\nNice TO have: \n\n1.\n2. ",
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "8H3N70OTeWdSdAU1DwpUz",
      "originalText": "FUNCTIONAL REQUIREMENTS: 1Min\n\nIn-SCOPE: \n1. saving customer payment details\n 2.  Making payment (in-flow)\n3. Payment outflow to sponsored partners\n4. Option to reuse / add\n5. Analytics dashboard\nLeast, most, how many times\n\nNice TO have: \n\n1.\n2. ",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.35
    },
